      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POSH WHEELS (8) is a first starter from the Brenda Oakey yard by Kinloch Brae out of She's Got Wheels. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Betting to provide the best guide to her chances. ADHANA DEREK (2) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing sixth (31.70) at this track in a Maiden. Expected to bounce back to best. ADHANA REMI (4) is still a maiden after nine runs but rarely far away, the latest finishing out of the placings when fourth at this track. Was prominent throughout latest and faded only late. Likely to be thereabouts. PHOTO CRUSHER (6) is by Photo Man out of Golden Skyrocket making debut. Can sneak into the frame with the right run.",
